rows.label: tlk42300042_04_msg0001
rows.name: Thanks to friends for taking up mission.

rows.label: tlk42300042_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Truth is, Ponpon actually spy for
Invidian military.

rows.label: tlk42300042_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Am monitoring situation in Fons Maim in secret and reporting findings
back to army.

rows.label: tlk42300042_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Drunk mercenaries always let snatches
of important information slip.

rows.label: tlk42300042_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Ponpon also instructed to find fresh
new recruits for Invidian army.

rows.label: tlk42300042_04_msg0006
rows.name:
Basically, job is all about gathering
of intelligence.

rows.label: tlk42300042_04_msg0007
rows.name:
Naturally, Ponpon know all about what
friends up to. That how he was able to
convey request from military!
